      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait sorry, i think i misunderstood the \"three semitones\" part. if C to G is a perfect fifth, isn't that more than three semitones? also you mentioned it's a \"closed loop\"—does that mean there's some kind of repeating pattern or logic behind why it's a circle instead of just a straight line of notes?",
